<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236728>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23 – 36. 23 – 24. Scleronotus virgatus, holotype, male: 23. Head, frontal; 24. Lateral habitus. 25 – 27. Oreodera casariae, holotype male: 25. Dorsal habitus; 26. Lateral habitus; 27. Head, frontal view. 28 – 31. Psapharochrus langeri, holotype male: 28. Dorsal habitus; 29. Ventral habitus; 30. Lateral habitus; 31. Head, frontal view. 32 – 35. Aegomorphus mexicanus, holotype male: 32. Dorsal habitus; 33. Ventral habitus; 34. Lateral habitus; 35. Head, frontal view. 36. Lamacoscylus albatus, holotype female, head, frontal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/236728/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

